rows.label: tlk41100171_03_msg0001
rows.name:
Tourists toss coins from Milama Viewpoint
into the Cloud Sea, so some of them
land over here.

rows.label: tlk41100171_03_msg0002
rows.name:
But the amount of money coming down
has gone down recently. I wonder if
everyone got bored of it?

rows.label: tlk41100171_03_msg0003
rows.name:
Well, with the money I've saved up,
I should be able to go back to Gula soon.
Maybe I'll leave with my dad...
